&gt;&gt; We started our own Python implementation because we felt that&#39;s easier
&gt;&gt; to extend and develop. I&#39;ve also taken a look at PyNEAT (another older
&gt;&gt; NEAT Python version) but I couldn&#39;t make it work. It seems that it&#39;s
